headline: CME Group Announces Record Volume, Open Interest Across Battery Metals Complex
summary: CME Group, the world's leading derivatives marketplace, today announced record volume and open interest across its battery metals complex. A total of 2,587 contracts were traded across battery metals futures and options on May 29, surpassing the previous record of 2,301 contracts set on February 11, 2025. Combined open interest also reached an all-time high of 64,387 contracts.
